Name: Dusk Warlocks
About the game: BATTLE YOUR FRIENDS Dusk Warlocks is an online multiplayer spellcasting game in which up to 4 players compete in an unforgiving tactical battle. Learn how different spells work with one another and come up with cool spell combos . Your objective is to capture the energy crystal before other players kill you or kill the player that is currently trying to capture it. BUILD YOUR SPELL ARSENAL The spells you use, that's completely up to you! Spells are categorized into 7 elements: Fire, Water, Ice, Air, Stone, Wood and Electricity . Every element has many spells to choose from, which makes the possible combinations almost endless. Pick out the 3 elements you want to fight with and equip 2 spells to each. CREATE YOUR WARLOCK Dusk Warlocks features 30+ different characters as well as thousands of unique spell combinations that allow you to make your Warlock feel unique and personalized.
